<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Daily To-Do List</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>My Daily To-Do List</h1>

    <p>Plan your day and stay organized!</p>

    <h3>Tasks:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Wake up early</li>
        <li>Exercise</li>
        <li>Attend classes</li>
        <li>Complete assignments</li>
        <li>Spend time with family</li>
        <li>Read a book</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Add New Task:</h3>
    <form>
        <label>Task Name:</label><br>
        <input type="text" name="task"><br><br>

        <input type="submit" value="Add Task">
    </form>

    <p>Stay productive and have a great day </p>

</body>
</html>
